cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper discusses image restoration using deep learning techniques, specifically image denoising and single image super-resolution. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of convolutional networks, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with image processing (cs.MM) and optimization (cs.NE) techniques.
